Class Invoice

public class Invoice extends Serializable
The Invoice class represents an invoice containing information such as buyer ID, renter ID, bus rating, timestamp, and payment status. Extends the Serializable class for serialization purposes.

Two constructors are provided: one that takes buyer ID and renter ID as parameters and another that takes Account and Renter objects for ease of use.

The bus rating and payment status are represented as enums BusRating and PaymentStatus, respectively.
